Individual




Charles A. Degliomini



Mr. Charles A. Degliomini is Executive VP-Government Affairs & Communications at Empire Resorts, Inc. He is on the Board of Directors at New York Gaming Association, Hudson Valley Economic Development Corp., and Boys & Girls Clubs of Town of Wallkill, Inc.
Mr. Degliomini was previously employed as Chief of Staff by US General Services Administration, President by Atlantic Communications, Inc., and Senior Vice President-Sales & Marketing by eLottery, Inc.
He received his undergraduate degree from Queens College.



